{"tid":558663,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好以為2月14約到人出黎就代表啲咩","createTime":"2018-02-12T12:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T13:52:47.000Z","uid":105472,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3bc7ead0d3bdbac1c74310bffe2d8664ef90442a","tid":558663,"uid":105472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"我兩個月前平安夜約到自己鍾意嘅女仔出黎<br />\n<br />\n佢上埋我屋企睇戲 我送埋佢返大埔<br />\n<br />\n之後亦表左白 但其實佢只係當我普通朋友<br />\n<br />\n根本唔想拍拖 最後連朋友都做唔成<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n我只係想同大家講<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為人地2月14日肯同你出街<br />\n<br />\n就會有咩含意 哩個世界冇必然<br />\n<br />\n但我亦由衷希望大家蜜運成功<br />\n<br />\nQuote: A big guy falls, he falls hard."},{"pid":"e34ccc2850c0cb1c3dbc69db454a043870448bf7","tid":558663,"uid":105472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"我後日好得閒"},{"pid":"9fa60ee1807fa56f4e5b0ab9a8f84e4633537515","tid":558663,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46a9e76a2049e53e153b23d1b7d6fe8becf26d16","tid":558663,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa60ee1807fa56f4e5b0ab9a8f84e4633537515","tid":558663,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"上得屋企唔做野，係人都say no la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760acafbcacdfa788018f945478735e434283302","tid":558663,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"喂，啊哥！你照下鏡先啦。"},{"pid":"83d7103f2be00a75d866cc19e4b06ea7ec3a3dcd","tid":558663,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"毒撚約到出街咪又係幫手拎下野"},{"pid":"3bbbac8919671ef5703855589222689516efdb50","tid":558663,"uid":38707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"平安夜<img src=\"/